<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>ROLLBACK</refname>
  <refpurpose>abort the current transaction</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>ROLLBACK</refname>
  <refpurpose>中止当前事务</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>

 <refsynopsisdiv>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<synopsis>
ROLLBACK [ WORK | TRANSACTION ]
</synopsis>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<synopsis>
ROLLBACK [ WORK | TRANSACTION ]
</synopsis>
 </refsynopsisdiv>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Description</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>描述</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   <command>ROLLBACK</command> rolls back the current transaction and causes
   all the updates made by the transaction to be discarded.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   <command>ROLLBACK</command>回滚当前事务并且导致
   该事务所作的所有更新都被抛弃。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Parameters</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>参数</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
    <term><literal>WORK</literal></term>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
    <term><literal>WORK</literal></term>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
    <term><literal>TRANSACTION</literal></term>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
    <term><literal>TRANSACTION</literal></term>
    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
     <para>
      Optional key words. They have no effect.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      可选关键词，没有效果。
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Notes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>注解</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   Use <xref linkend="SQL-COMMIT"> to
   successfully terminate a transaction.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   使用<xref linkend="SQL-COMMIT"/>可成功地终止一个事务。
  </para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   Issuing <command>ROLLBACK</> outside of a transaction
   block emits a warning and otherwise has no effect.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   在一个事务块之外发出<command>ROLLBACK</command>会发出一个
   警告并且不会有效果。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Examples</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>示例</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   To abort all changes:
<programlisting>
ROLLBACK;
</programlisting></para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   要中止所有更改：
<programlisting>
ROLLBACK;
</programlisting></para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Compatibility</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>兼容性</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>
   The SQL standard only specifies the two forms
   <literal>ROLLBACK</literal> and <literal>ROLLBACK
   WORK</literal>. Otherwise, this command is fully conforming.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   SQL 标准只指定了
   <literal>ROLLBACK</literal>和<literal>ROLLBACK
   WORK</literal>两种形式。除此之外，这个命令完全符合
   标准。
  </para>
 </refsect1>

